name: LEGENDS NEVER DIE #1
description:
Collage piece v.1.
5400x7200 px

Legends Never Die is part of a series of two that I launch simultaneously, a work that has a very particular process since when I was creating them I found the sad news that the legend Scratch had died that same day (August 29) That's why I felt that it gave another meaning to the project and I decided to take two different pieces when I was finishing today, although before it was only going to be one and make a series of 2. RIP Lee “Scratch” Perry.
